    <p>Managed IT eliminates that cost structure. You pay a fixed monthly amount that covers monitoring, maintenance, unlimited support and scheduled visits. Issues are identified and resolved before they become outages. When something does go wrong, it is fixed the same day rather than waiting days for a technician to become available. The productivity your team retains across a year of proactive IT management consistently delivers a return that is multiples of the monthly plan cost.</p>

